pan>** __between Israel and Hezbullah **<span style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="background: yellow;">escalates and there are heavy Israeli</span> civilian <span style="background: yellow;">casualties</span></span>** as a result of missile attacks launched on Israeli cities by Hezbullah. **<span style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">In that case, <span style="background: yellow;">Israel would</span></span>** of course **<span style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="background: yellow;">strike back with double the force on Lebanon. Such a war would quickly draw in Syria</span></span>**<span style="background: yellow;"> **<span style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">and</span>**</span> very possibly **<span style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="background: yellow;">Iran</span></span>**__<span style="font-size: 7pt;">. </span></span></span>
